###Create order
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/create-order/

{
  "cus_id": 4,
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": 13,
      "qty": 1
    },
    {
      "product_id": 2,
      "qty": 1
    },
    {
      "product_id": 10,
      "qty": 1
    }
  ],
  "shipping_cost": 45
}

### Get all order 
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders

### Get order by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/16

###get order + item
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/order_items/16

### Cancel Order
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/16/cancel

###เปลี่ยนสถานะ order (confirmed, shipping, delivery)
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders/16/status?status=cancelled


