###Search product
#ค้นหาทั่วไป + Sort ราคาต่ำ - สูง
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/search

{
  "query": "เสื้อ",
  "sort_by": "price_low",
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 20
}

### Filter by Brand
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/search

{
  "brand": "Uniqlo",
  "page": 1
}

###Filter by Category
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/search

{
  "category_id": 1,
  "sort_by": "price_high",
  "page": 1
}

###Filter by Tags
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/products/search

{
  "tags": ["หมวก"],
  "sort_by": "newest",
  "page": 1
}